<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4>Hello <%= @name %>,</h4>
    <p>
      You have a report for your area. Please check. Details below:
      <br />
      <p>
        User Reporting: <%= @report.user.username %></br>
        Area: <%= @report.intersection.area.name %></br>
        Desc: <%=@report.description%></br>
        <% @report.location.each do |loc| -%>
          Long Lat: <%=loc%></br>
        <% end -%>
      </p>
    </p>
    <p>
      Your next step is to log in to <%= @home_url %> and signoff on the area.
      Contact us for any questions and queries.<br /> <br />This email is auto generated by <code>Bunjil</code>, do not reply.
      If you believe you have recieved this email by mistake simply delete it.
      <br/><br/>

      
      Regards, <i>The Bunjil Forest Watch Dev Team</i></p>
  </body>
</html>